SYNOPSIS
    P_EXTRALOOK  "Extralook"

    string Set(P_EXTRALOOK, string look)
    string Query(P_EXTRALOOK)

DESCRIPTION
    The value is a string which is added to the P_LONG description of the
    living carrying the object.

EXAMPLE
    Set(P_EXTRALOOK, "A bright light hovers above him.\n");

AVAILABILITY
    Include: <properties.h>

    Availability: all things.

SEE ALSO
    thing(S)
